query:
INSERT INTO product_categories (productId, categoryId)
SELECT p.id, 12
FROM products p
WHERE p.brand = 'Thermo Fisher' AND p.name LIKE '%TG-%'
AND NOT EXISTS (
  SELECT 1 FROM product_categories pc WHERE pc.productId = p.id AND pc.categoryId = 12
);
